title._content: Barstow, Zedekiah S. of Keene NH

description._content: TITLE Barstow, Zedekiah S. of Keene NH CREATOR SUBJECT Men - NH - Keene Clergy - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of Zedekiah Smith Barstow of Keene New Hampshire. Zedekiah was born in 1790 in Canterbury CT and died in Keene in 1873. Dr. Barstow graduated from Yale and Dartmouth and was ordained in 1818. He started the Cheshire Theological Institute and was the last minister settled by the town before the separation of civil and church authority. He officiated until he was 80 years old. He was married to Elizabeth Fay Blake.
